function shadow(): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_mount_shadow()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Increments the shadow count on <code>mount</code>. Usually used by
<link xref="Gio.VolumeMonitor"/> implementations when creating a shadow mount for
<code>mount</code>, see <link xref="Gio.Mount.is_shadowed"/> for more information. The caller
will need to emit the <link xref="Gio.Mount-changed"/> signal on <code>mount</code> manually.</p>
